# 🌍 **Advanced Audio Translator** 🎙️🔊

A full-stack web application that allows users to **upload audio files** for speech-to-text transcription and **convert text to speech** with a modern, interactive UI.

---
Flask
    Backend web framework for handling routes & forms	
         pip install Flask
gTTS	
    Google Text-to-Speech for generating audio	
        pip install gtts


![Home Page](screenshots/screen(96).png)


Werkzeug	
    Utility for Flask's internal operations (included)	
        (Installed with Flask)
![Home Page](screenshots/ho.png)
