## 🔥 **Features**

- 📂 **Upload Audio File** → Get speech-to-text transcription.  
- ✏️ **Enter Text for TTS** → Convert text into speech audio.  
- 🎨 **Modern UI** → Beautiful, responsive design.  
- 🌍 **Multi-language Support** → Supports multiple languages for TTS.  

---

## ⚙️ **Tech Stack & Libraries**

### 🖥 **Frontend**  
- **HTML5** – Structure  
- **CSS3** – Styling (Glassmorphism design)  
- **JavaScript** – Interactive elements (basic)  

### 🖥 **Backend**  
- **Python 3.9+**  
- **Flask** – Lightweight web framework  
- **gTTS (Google Text-to-Speech)** – Converts text to audio  

### 📦 **Dependencies**

```bash
Flask
gtts

     
    🧠 Workflow & Algorithm

🔄 Speech-to-Text (STT) (Placeholder Logic)
📂 Upload audio file.
🔄 Simulate transcription (replaceable with models like Whisper or Google STT).
📝 Display the transcribed text.

 
    🔄 Text-to-Speech (TTS)

✏️ User inputs text.
🛠 gTTS converts text to audio.
🎧 The generated audio is embedded in the UI for playback.


   📝 How to Use  

Visit the Website 🌐
Upload Audio 🎙️ → Click Upload & Translate to transcribe audio.
Text to Speech 🔊 → Enter text and click Convert to Speech.
Listen to Audio 🎧 → Play generated audio directly on the page.


Project Structure
AdvancedAudioTranslator/
├── app.py               # Flask backend
├── requirements.txt     # Python dependencies
├── runtime.txt          # Python version for deployment
├── static/              # CSS & generated audio files
│   ├── style.css
│   └── tts_output.mp3
├── templates/
│   └── index.html       # Frontend UI
└── uploads/             # Uploaded audio files


